## Arrays

Tulpar supports both mixed-type arrays and type-safe arrays.

```tulpar
// Type-safe arrays
arrayInt numbers = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5];
arrayStr names = ["Ali", "Veli", "Ayşe"];

